WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.900 --> 00:00:04.795
Bu savolga javob berish va tanlashingiz mumkin 
bo‘lishi uchun, keling, ikkalasini taqqoslaylik.

00:00:04.795 --> 00:00:08.620
LinearLayouts ko‘rinishlarni satrlar yoki ustunlar bo‘yicha tekislash uchun juda yaxshi.

00:00:08.620 --> 00:00:11.840
Ular tartib vaznidan foydalangan holda joylarni

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:15.590
tarkib hajmiga qarab taqsimlash, ko‘rinishlarni kengaytirish yoki qisqartirish uchun yaxshi.

00:00:15.590 --> 00:00:17.615
Boshqa tomondan, RelativeLayout lar 

00:00:17.615 --> 00:00:20.200
elementlar joylashuvini 
bir-biriga nisbatan aniqlash uchun yaxhsi. 

00:00:20.200 --> 00:00:24.450
Masalan, B ni A dan pastga, yoki
chap burchakda C ni qo‘yish kabilar uchun.

00:00:25.545 --> 00:00:28.600
 RelativeLayout yordamida
ko‘rinishlarni bir-biri ustida joylashtirish ham oson.

00:00:28.600 --> 00:00:31.551
Masalan,
Bu yerda A ko‘rinishi B bilan mos keladi.

00:00:31.551 --> 00:00:35.545
Bizning tabriknomamizda gorizontal yoki vertikal ko‘rinishlar chizig‘i aslida yo‘q.

00:00:35.545 --> 00:00:38.169
Ko‘rib turganingizdek,
ushbu ko‘rinishlarning ba’zilari 
bir-biri ustida joylashgan.

00:00:38.169 --> 00:00:41.686
Shunday qilib, bu holda,
 RelativeLayout ko‘proq ma’noga ega.

00:00:41.686 --> 00:00:43.109
Va RelativeLayout bilan,

00:00:43.109 --> 00:00:47.080
Men bu ikkita TextView ni joylashtirish uchun uning o‘ziga xos xususiyatlaridan foydalanishim mumkin.

00:00:47.080 --> 00:00:49.230
Bular haqida shunchaki gapirish o‘rniga

00:00:49.230 --> 00:00:51.480
keyingi bir nechta savolda menga endi 
nima qilish kerakligini ayting.

